Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽…苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是叙述我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断战斗之宿命的序章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第68话 给七宝充满愤怒的挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战书已经确实送到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻终于来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我红龙是多么的期盼这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请以身为雷兽一族最后一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发挥全力奋战到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  给七宝殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上雷兽一族的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正要求和你决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日傍晚我在雷鸣谷等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们将性命不保
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是挑战书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷鸣谷的话  就在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先前雷兽兄弟住的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是飞天满天的亲戚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然送这种东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙胆子真不小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要随便看别人的信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这件事好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果为了报雷兽一族的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不是七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是直接跟那两人\N交手的犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是因为犬夜叉只是半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽根本看不上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算和这个\N叫做苍天的雷兽决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了替父亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到在那之前\N就出现了找我报仇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是战斗之人的宿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在耍什么帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少因为自己没办法耍帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里酸葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么需要我助你一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你打个折…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有需要的话别客气尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要介绍美女给我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事\N我都不会帮你忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区的雷兽我马上就打跑他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是雷兽兄弟住过的山谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不寻常的妖气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那里天气恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  不要逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们帮你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受决斗的我面子该往哪摆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你那张光会说的嘴挨打之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子根本不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才您一直在写什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要老是飘在那  过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是这次的作战书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢牢的记在脑子里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是堂堂正正的决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这么可爱的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打赢\N那些穷凶恶极的邪魔歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫弥勒的法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有什么都能吸进去的风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫珊瑚的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是驱魔的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她还收服了一只\N叫做云母的妖怪猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为全都是我去调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是这个犬夜叉\N与戈薇是最强的双人组
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道有多少妖怪被他们打败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面冲突的话我就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽一族就会完全毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就这样隐居起来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是我最大的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要找七宝要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再咯哩叭唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去实行战术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经来到这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要边发抖边走路啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别激动别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话傍晚之前会到不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战书不是这样子写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个只能念“七宝”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有别的念法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如“犬夜叉”之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连自己的名字都不会念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是确认一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦  没错  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给我的挑战书啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧  苍天  我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝…你根本没有前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们大家听好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的不用出手帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要帮你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是穷凶恶极的雷兽一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快找个安全的地方避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~好~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚与弥勒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常希望我们帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白的拜托不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先利用大岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将七宝和犬夜叉他们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行的很顺利呢  苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了  我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个迷糊虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逮到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  快点放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来得正好  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种杂碎对我没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫老大出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去叫雷兽一族的苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没骗人  看就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是看了不知道才问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有闲功夫跟小鬼玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我当成小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好东西嘛  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  明明就是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  我可是了不起的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要咯哩叭唆  把那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说给我就给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不要就是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两人根本就还是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙  你还有事情要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是的  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要封住云母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是妖怪但是猫还是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用木天蓼应该就能迷住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歪脑筋动得还真快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气味是木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是对方的陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子接下来得用走的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们  请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师  这有点可疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  我是遵循着佛道之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是任何情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法眼睁睁看着\N有困难的人不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会高兴的接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是大好人呢  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒的弱点就是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而珊瑚绝不会丢下弥勒不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用这一点就能制服他们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦…请你再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我当然会过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师不要这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  方便的话将原委…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就跟你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是法师害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑拨对我是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送这个来的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是引诱你出来的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么对付我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要慢慢折磨你到死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭吧  喊叫吧  怕的浑身发抖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会逃避决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你厉害识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的头脑聪明得很
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了弥补弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已设下\N如此天衣无缝的战术了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太肮脏了  你这卑劣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是靠同伴帮忙的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有拜托他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们自己要跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再找借口了  胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我胆小鬼  卑劣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小胆小胆小胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙卑劣卑劣卑劣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒他们在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉最怕的\N就是戈薇的“坐下”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招一定管用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下坐下坐下坐下坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么戈薇的“坐下”没有效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是把那个当作是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里像了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  投降了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  你才该快点投降呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你拿的画笔好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是戈薇送给我的\N叫做蜡笔的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系  小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许可以考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要好想要好想要好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会上你的当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要慢慢的宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么决斗赢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以得到这蜡笔  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子也许是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是稀奇  会飞的蛇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少装模作样了  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是雷兽的使魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有礼貌!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是大名鼎鼎龙族的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说不要装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  只要再一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你当我的头是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  这样就能逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  就别再欺负他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也蛮可怜的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要同情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说我也是龙族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打的话尽量打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有些优点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  反而自找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝也在那里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会说那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要打头三次就能变身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶\N来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就来这招不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的  没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙竟然没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  犬夜叉  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟了吗  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是云  风之伤也不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在  先收拾这小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么  雷击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  想不到你还蛮强的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说  你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  现在开始要认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中了我的箭也撑不了多久的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那光箭只是中看不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  这怎么可能  接招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到也无所谓  刺一下手看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿来治肩酸也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是老太婆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有逃走算你倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙\N只要揍三下就能变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少装蒜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好过分喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你就带我们去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫苍天的所在的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两把刷子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐妖术  旋转独乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽幻术  达摩不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此只好使出爱哭香菇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就用爆笑粟子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天  你就放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性命跟蜡笔哪一个比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙  你失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  苍天少主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  该不会就是这小子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是对我下挑战书的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幕后主使苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  不要把我当小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是雷兽一族之长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~好~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  不要摸我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这小鬼\N我们就忙的不可开交
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过不需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟弟  你几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女生吗  那更可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你不要摸我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她居然是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有够可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  七宝  你想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是承认输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子就当个好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再想什么报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样我的死斗结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功切断了复仇的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那穷凶恶极的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍天跟红龙也受到了教训
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不敢找我决斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成长了一大步或二大步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更强的敌人等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我不能驻足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能回首过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是背负着战斗之宿命的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子汉的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再耍帅了  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  犬夜叉欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬~夜~叉~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.46,0:22:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:21.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:28.20,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:35.02,ED,,0,0,0,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:42.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:48.32,ED,,0,0,0,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:55.40,ED,,0,0,0,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:02.15,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:08.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:15.82,ED,,0,0,0,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:22.50,ED,,0,0,0,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:29.12,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:35.75,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:39.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  那家伙怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对大家说了你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:23:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而让误会更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是管那些事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的分身又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是误解归误解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只是觉得你是个不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙展开了无尽的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从很多人身上夺走了脸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖的无脸男人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“不凉少黏”是什么啊（不良少年）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:20.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,雷兽一族的幸存者{\pos(290,291)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:20.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,为了替飞天满天报仇\N挑战了七宝 其实是女孩子{\pos(270,438)}
